snippet.title: Farsight
snippet.description:
Remote viewing is a mental process developed by the U.S. military and used for espionage. The Farsight Institute is the leading civilian research and educational venue for the serious scientific study of the remote-viewing phenomenon. Here you find full public studies using remote viewing to explore history, our planet, and other worlds. Farsight also has a public educational mission, and we offer an extensive and free video instructional library on remote viewing methods. To learn more about remote viewing, visit our web site at https://www.farsight.org . 

Our logo is a swirling circular pattern that has a rising element at the top. The circular pattern represents humanity on Earth in a state of confusion, while the rising element at the top is humanity emerging out of this confusion as it looks forward to seize a bold and positive destiny among other civilizations in the cosmos.

You help us by subscribing to our YouTube channel.
